<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1078/77 of 17 May 1977 introducing a system of premiums for the non-marketing of milk and milk products and for the conversion of dairy herds (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1041/78 (2), and in particular Article 7 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 17. mai 1977. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1078/77, millega kehtestatakse lisatasude s&uuml;steem piima ja piimatoodete turustamata j&auml;tmise ja l&uuml;psikarjade &uuml;mberkorraldamise eest, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1041/78, (2) eriti selle artiklit 7, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas application of the system of premiums for the non-marketing of milk and milk products and for the conversion of dairy herds has been extended; whereas certain conditions laid down in Regulation (EEC) No 1078/77 have been amended; whereas, therefore, Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1307/77 of 15 June 1977 laying down rules for the application of the system of premiums for the non-marketing of milk and milk products and the conversion of dairy herds (3), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 689/78 (4), should be amended accordingly, whereas experience requires that some of the rules should be clarified so as to assist their application; whereas, for the sake of clarity, it would appear advisable to repeal Regulation (EEC) No 1307/77 and to adopt a new text incorporating the provisions of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 36/78 of 9 January 1978 on certain special cases as regards the application of the system of premiums for the non-marketing of milk and milk products and for the conversion of dairy herds (5); </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: piima ja piimatoodete turustamata j&auml;tmise ja l&uuml;psikarjade &uuml;mberkorraldamise jaoks makstavate lisatasude s&uuml;steemi kohaldamist on pikendatud; teatavaid m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 1078/77 s&auml;testatud tingimusi on muudetud; seep&auml;rast tuleks vastavalt muuta komisjoni 15. juuni 1977. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1307/77, milles s&auml;testatakse eeskirjad piima ja piimatoodete turustamata j&auml;tmise ja l&uuml;psikarjade &uuml;mberkorraldamise jaoks makstavate lisatasude s&uuml;steemi kohaldamiseks, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 689/78; (4) kogemused on n&auml;idanud, et seejuures tuleks m&otilde;ningaid eeskirju nende kohaldamise h&otilde;lbustamiseks t&auml;psustada; selguse huvides oleks soovitav tunnistada kehtetuks m&auml;&auml;rus (EM&Uuml;) nr 1307/77 ning v&otilde;tta vastu uus tekst, millega liidetakse komisjoni 9. jaanuari 1978. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 36/78 (piima ja piimatoodete turustamata j&auml;tmise ja l&uuml;psikarjade &uuml;mberkorraldamise jaoks makstavate lisatasude s&uuml;steemi kohaldamise teatavate erijuhtude kohta) (5) s&auml;tted; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to ensure that a check can be kept throughout the period to which the obligations under the scheme relate, it is necessary to know not only the numbers of dairy cows but also the numbers of all-female animals suitable for milk production; whereas all such animals must therefore be registered and marked and their particulars entered on an identity card, by means of which it may be checked whether the use of the animal has been in accordance with the rules; whereas, however, since a system of identity cards is open to abuse in the event of the animals being sold, it is desirable that it be made clear to farmers that they are to be responsible for its return, thus ensuring that they will not sell their animals without making the necessary provisions for the card to be returned to them; </inglise>
<eesti> kontrolli tagamiseks kogu kavaga seotud kohustuste t&auml;itmise ajal on vaja teada mitte ainult l&uuml;psilehmade arvu, vaid ka k&otilde;igi piima tootmiseks sobilike lehmade arvu; seep&auml;rast peavad k&otilde;ik sellised loomad olema registreeritud ja m&auml;rgistatud ning nende andmed kantud identifitseerimiskaardile, mille alusel on v&otilde;imalik kontrollida, kas looma on kasutatud vastavalt eeskirjadele; kuna loomade m&uuml;&uuml;gi korral on identifitseerimiskaartide s&uuml;steemi v&otilde;imalik kuritarvitada, on soovitav talupidajatele selgitada, et nad peavad vastutama identifitseerimiskaardi tagastamise eest, millega tagatakse kaardi tagastamine loomade m&uuml;&uuml;gi korral; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas in order to avoid any extra administrative work, existing national marks and identity cards may be used, cross-frontier trade is not involved; </inglise>
<eesti> v&auml;ltimaks t&auml;iendavat haldust&ouml;&ouml;d, v&otilde;ib kasutada olemasolevaid riiklikke m&auml;rgistusi ja identifitseerimiskaarte, v&auml;lja arvatud &uuml;hendusesisese kaubanduse puhul; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, for the purposes of the conversion premium, the number of the various animals which the farmer may keep on his holding must be calculated in terms of a livestock unit equal to one adult bovine animal; whereas, since a change in the herd may be caused by seasonal factors or by the replacement of animals, without affecting the farmer's ability to fulfil his obligation, the number of livestock units should be calculated for each year in such a way that animals kept for a short period and animals whose classification changes in the course of the year as a result of age are counted on a year basis; </inglise>
