<inglise> Whereas regular communications from the Member States as to the number of applications submitted and approved are necessary in order that a check may be kept on the operation of the premium system and its uniform application; whereas such communications are also necessary for purposes of the report to the Council provided for in Article 13 of Regulation (EEC) No 1078/77; </inglise>
