<inglise> Article 10 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 10 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Where the recipient of the premium acquires, during the period to which his undertakings apply, a holding supplying milk or milk products or part of such a holding, this shall not entail the extension of the undertakings to the acquired areas, provided that: </inglise>
